### 获取热门数据集列表（按热度排序）
# @name getPopularDatasets
GET http://localhost:8080/api/statistics/datasets/popular?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 获取热门研究学科列表（按热度排序）
# @name getPopularSubjects
GET http://localhost:8080/api/statistics/subjects/popular?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 获取特定数据集的热度值
# @name getDatasetPopularity
GET http://localhost:8080/api/statistics/datasets/popularity?datasetId={{datasetId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 获取特定研究学科的热度值
# @name getSubjectPopularity
GET http://localhost:8080/api/statistics/subjects/popularity?subjectId={{subjectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 获取公开数据集列表（批量查询，不会增加热度）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/datasets?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 获取特定公开数据集（会增加数据集和对应学科的热度）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/datasets/{{datasetId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 获取特定数据集的时间轴（会增加数据集和对应学科的热度）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/datasets/{{datasetId}}/timeline
Authorization: Bearer {{platformAdminToken}}

### 获取所有激活的研究学科列表（批量查询，不会增加热度）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/research-subjects
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 获取特定研究学科（会增加研究学科热度）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/research-subjects/{{subjectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{datasetUploaderToken}}